A young man, Azeez Morufu has been arrested for collecting money from an Automated Teller Machine, (ATM) points of one of the new generation banks beside Radio Nigeria, Dugbe, Ibadan, Oyo State without using a card. The young man said to possess high criminal instinct confessed that the incident was not the first time he would be carrying out the nefarious act. Speaking to newsmen Morufu said he had a code he always input on the ATM to dispense without a card. Morufu Azeez met his waterloo when a passer-by saw him with a huge amount of money at the machine. The witness explained that she became suspicious when he noticed the young man in dirty clothes withdrawing huge amount from the ATM. The suspect has however been handed over the police. 